-- Daimler May Consider Acquisitions in Commercial-Vehicle Segment, CEO Says
-- B y   C h r i s   R e i t e r
-- 2010-09-30T09:36:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-30/daimler-may-consider-acquisitions-in-commercial-vehicle-segment-ceo-says.html
Daimler AG may consider making
acquisitions in the commercial-vehicle segment, Chief Executive
Officer Dieter Zetsche said at the Paris Motor Show today.
Daimler isn’t in talks with Fiat SpA about the Italian
carmaker’s industrial unit, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
